            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日，微软推出了一系列以经典 Windows XP 墙纸为灵感的新产品，包括适用于 PC 和智能手机的墙纸以及限量版的环保主题冷衫。这些创意产品在 Xbox Gear Shop 上架，吸引了 Windows 爱好者的广泛关注。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207551 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/00-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/00-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/00-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/00.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://gigazine.net/gsc_news/en/20231129-windows-xp-wallpaper-sweater">Gigazine</a></p><p>这批全新的 Windows XP 墙纸可以通过官方<a href="https://gear.xbox.com/pages/windows">连结</a>免费下载，提供了适合 PC 的横向桌布和适合智能手机的墙纸。桌布以 ZIP 格式发布，其中除了原始的 Windows XP 风格墙纸外，还包括三张绘画风格的排列墙纸，桌面墙纸、手机墙纸解像度为 1920 x 1080。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_OGDesktopWallpaper-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_OGDesktopWallpaper-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_OGDesktopWallpaper-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_OGDesktopWallpaper-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_OGDesktopWallpaper-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_OGDesktopWallpaper.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_PencilSketchDesktopWallpaper-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bliss_PencilSketchDesktopWallpaper-6