            <title>米哈游聘《原神》鸿蒙开发员，或成鸿蒙 OS 大作游戏先锋</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/03/game-developer-mihoyo-is-recruiting-genshin-impact-engine-development-specialists/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=game-developer-mihoyo-is-recruiting-genshin-impact-engine-development-specialists</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/03/game-developer-mihoyo-is-recruiting-genshin-impact-engine-development-specialists/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 07:03:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[原神]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[米哈游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[鸿蒙]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1207204</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日，知名游戏开发公司米哈游官方网站的招聘信息显示，米哈游正在寻找一名适合游戏《原神》的引擎开发（系统向）专员，这似乎预示著《原神》将与鸿蒙系统进行接轨。</p><p>根据图片显示，这一新职位主要聚焦于鸿蒙系统的 UI、输入、文件系统、内存管理等方面的适配工作，同时还包括对 CPU 和 GPU 的性能分析与优化。这一举措表明米哈游正致力于使其游戏更好地与鸿蒙系统进行整合。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-28-at-2.07.05 PM-600x580.png" alt="" width="600" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-28-at-2.07.05 PM-600x580.png 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-28-at-2.07.05 PM-931x900.png 931w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-28-at-2.07.05 PM-768x743.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-28-at-2.07.05 PM.png 1520w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></p><p>尽管华为在马来西亚的手机仍在使用 EMUI 操作系统，但其平板装置已经开始使用鸿蒙系统。这一转变可能意味著米哈游将对所有华为装置用户进行直接的系统适配，从而使他们能更便捷地享受到《原神》等游戏。</p><p>这一发展对于《原神》的粉丝群体以及华为装置用户来说无疑是一个好消息，它不仅提升了游戏的可及性，也可能为游戏的性能带来进一步的优化。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://zinggadget.com/2023/11/26/%e9%b8%bf%e8%92%99%ef%bc%8c%e5%90%af%e5%8a%a8%ef%bc%9f%e7%b1%b3%e5%93%88%e6%b8%b8%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b%e6%8b%9b%e8%81%98%e8%ae%a9%e5%8e%9f%e7%a5%9e%e9%80%82%e9%85%8d%e9%b8%bf%e8%92%99%e7%b3%bb%e7%bb%9f/">zinggadget</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

